title: GTX 2018 [Race, Eng, 2018]
description:
GTX Racing 2018 is your pass to the new world behind the wheel of the fastest and most beautiful cars in the world. You will experience a stunning sensation of speed. This car simulator provides an opportunity race the best machines from the last 30 years.  The choices are wide ranging, plus many options are available. Jump in your car and start winning races in order to open new tracks.

System:

ОС: Windows 7 +
CPU: 2 GHz
RAM: 512 mb
VRAM: 256 mb
HDD: 328 mb
